item.title: CVE-2015-1320|2024-08-06T04:40:18.463Z -- ubuntu -- maas
item.description: The SeaMicro provisioning of Ubuntu MAAS logs credentials, including username and password, for the management interface. This issue affects Ubuntu MAAS versions prior to 1.9.2.
